items.headline: Concise course for job-hunting and career development in the English-speaking world (for relocation or remote work)
objectives_summary: Yes, it is possible to be happy in your professional life, not just kill the time to pay bills. You can have a career that is both rewarding and well-paid. This course will explore your unique talents, equip you with practical strategies and create the sense of clarity, direction and strength within.

Career English is designed for you to face job-hunting in the English-speaking environment with confidence. For a non-native English speaker, it takes not just genuine professionalism, but self-awareness, analysis, self-presentation and negotiation skills.
